title: Nenu Local - Telugu Full Movie 2017.MP4
description:
Nenu Local (English: I'm local) is a 2017 Indian Telugu romantic comedy film directed by Trinadha Rao Nakkina and produced by Dil Raju under his banner Sri Venkateswara Creations. The film's story, screenplay and dialogues are written by Prasanna Kumar Bezawada. It features Nani and Keerthy Suresh in the lead roles. Music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad.The trailer of the film was launched on 14 January 2017. The film was released on 3 February 2017 with mostly positive reviews and went on to become a blockbuster at the box office. It also collected over 1 million dollars at the U.S. box office. The film was dubbed into Hindi as Super Khiladi 4 by Goldmines Telefilms Pvt. Ltd. and had a theatrical release on 17 November 2017. Dubbing artist Sanket Mhatre dubbed for Nani's voice and dubbing artist Chaitanya dubbed for Naveen Chandra's voice in the Hindi dubbed version. The film was remade in Bengali as Total Dadagiri with Yash Dasgupta
